      "value": "<div class=\"ddb\">\n<p>You touch a quiver containing arrows or bolts. When a target is hit by a ranged weapon attack using a piece of ammunition drawn from the quiver, the target takes an extra 1d6 &amp;Reference[fire]{fire} damage. The spellâ€™s magic ends on the piece of ammunition when it hits or misses, and the spell ends when twelve pieces of ammunition have been drawn from the quiver.</p>\n<p class=\"s19\"><strong>At Higher Levels.</strong> <span class=\"p\">When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 4th level or higher, the number of pieces of ammunition you can affect with this spell increases by two for each slot level above 3rd.</span></p>\n</div>",
